{"tid":1471256,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"插贓嫁禍好折墮 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:29:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2784810e19a4ebe1df00f0d2b9cdb6f7ab8db4bd","tid":1471256,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:26:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190814/20748299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F20748299&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3RkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=5d6e2c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190814%2F20748299&h=f4d69d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190814/20748299</a><br />\n<br />\n插贓嫁禍好折墮 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190814/large/1565691051_d3d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190814%2Flarge%2F1565691051_d3d8.jpg&h=2848aeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nnow新聞台截圖<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n8.11警暴恐襲，港人徹夜不眠，眼睜睜看着一個又一個年輕人被「毀」了，他／她們大多是走避不及，或遭佈局出賣。<br />\n<br />\n當日，黑幫北角之戰落空，示威者沒去送頭，不知是否開不到工收不足錢，白等躁狂只向小市民施暴，但各區浴血就怵目驚心，政警黑勾結，施襲者被放生，但警方的過期有毒催淚煙在民居濫發，槍彈直射示威者頭部，一位少女被射爆眼球失明，地鐵中以不必要武力濫打濫捕，已受制趴地落齒吐血者仍遭毒毆膝跪頭部&hellip;&hellip;賤招百出。<br />\n<br />\n最賤的是警員喬裝示威者設阱拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n本來卧底潛伏滲透並非意外，雨傘運動魚蛋革命中難道沒有？但不及反送中運動「慘烈」。無間道是警方對付為非作歹黑幫採用之破案手段。但現在施諸數百萬港人和平示威得不到林鄭毒蛾回應，有冤無路訴的年輕人身上，置諸死地。<br />\n<br />\n卧底可以在被捕者背包中塞竹枝、誣衊示威者為暴徒，大家會合理懷疑，這兩個月以來的撞破立會玻璃、掟磚、掟削尖鐵枝（早已準備好）、污損國徽、拋國旗落海、擲汽油彈、縱火（白警內幕消息）&hellip;&hellip;「重手」暴行，由二五仔製造、挑釁、煽動、加劇，入之以罪，抓捕鎮壓，助毒蛾及黑警高層以血續位。插贓嫁禍好折墮！  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n先跟精神科醫生真誠對話吧 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n誰令香港五勞七傷 (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"0dcada4897c533599fa9853002a2c4d8425b8760","tid":1471256,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:29:12.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n可以賽後檢討，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It is now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YvdK1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YvdK1E.jpg&h=e1c38679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D83Sf8j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD83Sf8j.jpg&h=da01072f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JSeBHOk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJSeBHOk.jpg&h=4d624e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7KeuxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&h=6eb7f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95FtyZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95FtyZg.jpg&h=ecc3ae69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caConSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaConSC.jpg&h=d1559671&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}